title: Destiny Chukunyere
text:
Destiny Chukunyere
Destiny Chukunyere MQR (born 29 August 2002) is a Maltese singer from Birkirkara, Malta. She won the Junior Eurovision Song Contest 2015, where she represented Malta with the song "Not My Soul". In 2017, she participated in the eleventh series of Britain's Got Talent where she finished 6th in the second semi-final and thus was eliminated.
